## Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all possible factors influencing organizational disasters. Additionally, the dynamic nature of disasters means that new risks may emerge that are not covered in this report. Further research and continuous monitoring of emerging threats are recommended for comprehensive disaster preparedness.